PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782341275
OL,3,CUK braced for record-breaking 40C as
OL,4,Cred weather warnings come into force
OL,6,FThese alerts are in place from 1am on
OL,7,FWednesday to 11pm on Thursday, and
OL,8,Fmean "adverse temperatures are likely
OL,9,Fto impact on the health and wellbeing
OL,10,Fof the population".
OL,12,FHow are schools impacted?
OL,14,FAlmost 100 schools in Somerset will be
OL,15,Ffully closed on Wednesday and
OL,16,FThursday, according to Somerset
OL,17,FCouncil.
OL,26,@pD@FOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
