OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782341275
OL,3,CUK braced for record-breaking 40C as
OL,4,Cred weather warnings come into force
OL,6,FAnd around 100 schools will be at
OL,7,Fleast partially closed over the next
OL,8,Ftwo days in Buckinghamshire, along
OL,9,Fwith 86 schools in Gloucestershire,
OL,10,Faccording to council data.
OL,12,FMany schools in Horsham, West Sussex,
OL,13,Fare closing early on Wednesday and
OL,14,FThursday, with some setting pupils
OL,15,Fwork to do at home.
OL,17,FSt John's Marlborough in Wiltshire
OL,18,Fsaid it would be shut all day on
OL,19,FWednesday and Thursday before re-
OL,20,Fopening on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782341275
OL,3,CUK braced for record-breaking 40C as
OL,4,Cred weather warnings come into force
OL,6,FOther schools in Sutton in south
OL,7,FLondon and Haringey in north London
OL,8,Fhave also been forced to close from
OL,9,FTuesday to Thursday.
OL,11,FHampshire County Council has listed 35
OL,12,Fschools which will at least partially
OL,13,Fclose because of the heat this week,
OL,14,Fwith a further seven in the
OL,15,FSouthampton area.
OL,17,FChildren at some schools have been
OL,18,Ftold they can wear PE kit rather than
OL,19,Ffull school uniform, which can involve
OL,20,Flong trousers and blazers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
