PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782341275
OL,3,CUK braced for record-breaking 40C as
OL,4,Cred weather warnings come into force
OL,6,FWhat about travel?
OL,8,FTransport bosses have urged people to
OL,9,Favoid travelling on Wednesday and
OL,10,FThursday and are warning those that do
OL,11,Fto "prepare for a disrupted journey".
OL,13,FNational Rail warned of disruption to
OL,14,FGatwick Express, Great Northern,
OL,15,FSouthern and Thameslink services until
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FAvanti West Coast said it planned to
OL,19,Frun fewer services than usual between
OL,20,FTuesday and Thursday, and that there
OL,21,Fwas "a risk of further disruption".
OL,26,@sD@DOUsD@dO]}D@EOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
